annotations.title: I Totes Stole The Name Of This Cocktail From A Smaller Weaker Cocktail

textContent:
1.5oz (45ml) Dill Infused Gin
.5oz (15ml) Peach Liqueur
.75oz (22.5ml) Orgeat
.75oz (22.5ml) Lemon Juice
Dill Flower Garnish

Shake and strain into rocks glass over large cube.
